<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.5">
<l>vaṇṇak karuṅkuḻa lāycciyāl mottuṇṭu</l>
<l>kaṇṇik kuṟuṅkayiṟṟāl kaṭṭuṇṭāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>kaṇṇik kuṟuṅkayiṟṟāl kaṭṭuṇṭā ṉākilum</l>
<l>eṇṇaṟ kariya ṉimaiyōrkkum cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! Having been beaten by a herdess with lovely dark curls,</l>
<l>He was tied with a short, knotted rope.</l>
<l>Although he was tied with a short knotted rope,</l>
<l>He is difficult for even unblinking [celestials] to reckon. Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
